  "title": "⭐ B2B Outreach Buddy (Fresh Grad Marketing)",
  "description": "<p>🎓 FRESH OUT OF SCHOOL OR ORD? START HERE! <br>\nMeet business clients, support corporate campaigns &amp; kickstart a real B2B career.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Your Role:</strong><br>\n•  Assist with business outreach &amp; F2F engagements<br>\n•  Help coordinate corporate marketing activities<br>\n• Gather feedback directly from clients<br>\n•  Pick up real-world presentation &amp; client skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why You’ll Love It:</strong><br>\n•  Fresh Grad / ORD Friendly — no experience needed<br>\n•  Supportive team + fun working culture<br>\n•  Hands-on learning in real B2B environments</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>💸 Weekly Pay + Incentives<br>\n📈 Build confidence in pitching &amp; client comms<br>\n🔥 A great entry into B2B marketing</p>",
